        "description": {
            "value": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Free Action\" aria-label=\"Free Action\">0</span></p><p><em>You’ve learned to fire then fade into Roshar’s harsh battlefields, keeping a safe distance from heavily armed enemies who might force hand-to-hand combat.</em></p><p>After you make a ranged attack, spend 2 focus to @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.wC4Z0mdGwRxLDpMC]{Disengage} as <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Free Action\" aria-label=\"Free Action\">0</span>. If you then end your turn in cover or an area where your enemy’s senses are obscured, you gain the benefit of the @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.I1CQjZicYdeG9NCN]{Brace} action.</p>",
            "chat": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Free Action\" aria-label=\"Free Action\">0</span></p><p>After making a ranged attack, spend 2 focus to @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.wC4Z0mdGwRxLDpMC]{Disengage} without spending <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Free Action\" aria-label=\"Free Action\">1</span>, and @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.I1CQjZicYdeG9NCN]{Brace} if you enter cover or obscured area.</p>",
            "short": "<p><strong>Activation:</strong> <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Free Action\" aria-label=\"Free Action\">0</span></p><p>After you make a ranged attack, spend 2 focus to @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.wC4Z0mdGwRxLDpMC]{Disengage} as <span class=\"cosmere-icon\" data-tooltip=\"Free Action\" aria-label=\"Free Action\">0</span>. If you then end your turn in cover or an area where your enemy’s senses are obscured, you gain the benefit of the @UUID[Compendium.cosmere-rpg.actions.Item.I1CQjZicYdeG9NCN]{Brace} action.</p>"
